---
// Contact Form Section - Premium two-column layout with trust indicators
---

<section id="contact" class="section contact-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <!-- Left Column: Info & Trust -->
      <div class="contact-info reveal-left">

        
        <div class="contact-intro">
          <p class="intro-lead">Y, llegados a este punto, ¿todavía te queda alguna duda?</p>
          <p>Si tienes claro que podemos ayudarte a alcanzar tus objetivos, contáctanos. Y, si no lo tienes claro, también. Porque explicar todo lo que podemos hacer como medical writers y consultores healthcare no es fácil.</p>
          <p>Escríbenos y nos pondremos en contacto contigo para ofrecerte la solución que necesites.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="line-divider"></div>
        
        <!-- Trust Indicators -->
        <div class="trust-indicators">

          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg class="trust-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-6-6z"></path>
              <path d="M14 3v5h5M16 13H8M16 17H8M10 9H8"></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Presupuesto sin compromiso</span>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-item">
            <svg class="trust-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
              <polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <span>Confidencialidad garantizada</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Right Column: Form -->
      <div class="contact-form-wrapper reveal-right">
        <div class="form-card">
          <form class="contact-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/YOUR_FORM_ID" method="POST">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name" class="visually-hidden">Nombre</label>
              <input 
                type="text" 
                id="name" 
                name="name" 
                class="form-control" 
                placeholder="Tu nombre" 
                required
              >
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email" class="visually-hidden">Email</label>
              <input 
                type="email" 
                id="email" 
                name="email" 
                class="form-control" 
                placeholder="Tu email" 
                required
              >
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="phone" class="visually-hidden">Teléfono</label>
              <input 
                type="tel" 
                id="phone" 
                name="phone" 
                class="form-control" 
                placeholder="Tu teléfono"
              >
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="message" class="visually-hidden">Mensaje</label>
              <textarea 
                id="message" 
                name="message" 
                class="form-control" 
                placeholder="¿En qué podemos ayudarte?" 
                rows="5"
                required
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="legal-1" name="legal-1" required>
              <label for="legal-1">
                Acepto la <a href="/politica-privacidad/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">política de privacidad</a>
              </label>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-checkbox">
              <input type="checkbox" id="legal-2" name="legal-2" required>
              <label for="legal-2">
                He leído y consiento el tratamiento de mis datos personales
              </label>
            </div>
            
            <p class="form-legal">
              <strong>Información básica sobre protección de datos:</strong><br>
              <strong>Responsable:</strong> Sinergias en Salud MCA SL<br>
              <strong>Finalidad:</strong> Gestión de la solicitud de información<br>
              <strong>Legitimación:</strong> Consentimiento del interesado<br>
              <strong>Destinatarios:</strong> No se ceden datos a terceros<br>
              <strong>Derechos:</strong> Acceso, rectificación, supresión, portabilidad, limitación, oposición, olvido
            </p>
            
            <button type="submit" class="btn form-submit btn-shimmer">
              <span>Enviar mensaje</span>
              <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
                <path d="M22 2L11 13M22 2l-7 20-4-9-9-4 20-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-section {
    position: relative;
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-body);
  }
  
  /* ===== GRID LAYOUT ===== */
  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  
  @media (min-width: 992px) {
    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
    }
  }
  
  /* ===== LEFT COLUMN: INFO ===== */
  .contact-info h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-heading);
  }
  
  .contact-intro {
    margin: 32px 0 40px;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  
  .intro-lead {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: var(--color-heading);
  }
  
  .contact-intro p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  
  /* ===== TRUST INDICATORS ===== */
  .trust-indicators {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg-subtle);
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-theme);
  }
  
  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }
  
  .trust-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }
  
  /* ===== RIGHT COLUMN: FORM ===== */
  .form-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-theme);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px;
    box-shadow: 
      0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08),
      0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .form-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }
  }
  
  .contact-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }
  
  .form-group {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .form-control {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 16px;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border-theme);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--color-bg-input);
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }
  
  .form-control:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: #95cca5;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(149, 204, 165, 0.15);
  }
  
  .form-control::placeholder {
    color: var(--color-text-muted-light);
  }
  
  textarea.form-control {
    min-height: 140px;
    resize: vertical;
  }
  
  /* ===== CHECKBOXES ===== */
  .form-checkbox {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }
  
  .form-checkbox input {
    margin-top: 3px;
    accent-color: #95cca5;
    width: 18px;
    height: 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  
  .form-checkbox label {
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  
  .form-checkbox a {
    color: #1a3865;
    text-decoration: underline;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
  }
  
  .form-checkbox a:hover {
    color: #95cca5;
  }
  
  .form-legal {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted-light);
    margin: 0 0 32px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--color-bg-subtle);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  
  /* ===== SUBMIT BUTTON ===== */
  .form-submit {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 8px;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  
  .btn-shimmer {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .btn-shimmer::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: -100%;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(
      90deg,
      transparent,
      rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
      transparent
    );
    animation: shimmer 3s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% { left: -100%; }
    50%, 100% { left: 100%; }
  }
  
  .form-submit svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .form-submit:hover svg {
    transform: translateX(5px) translateY(-3px);
  }
  
  /* ===== ACCESSIBILITY ===== */
  .visually-hidden {
    position: absolute;
    width: 1px;
    height: 1px;
    padding: 0;
    margin: -1px;
    overflow: hidden;
    clip: rect(0, 0, 0, 0);
    white-space: nowrap;
    border: 0;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .contact-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    
    .trust-indicators {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }

  /* ===== DARK MODE FIXES ===== */
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .contact-section {
    background-color: #1a3865 !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .contact-info h2,
  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .intro-lead {
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .contact-intro {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9) !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .trust-indicators {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) !important;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .trust-item {
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .form-card {
    background-color: #112645 !important;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .form-checkbox {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8) !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .form-legal {
    background: transparent !important;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5) !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .form-control {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2) !important;
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) !important;
    color: #ffffff !important;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .form-control::placeholder {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4) !important;
  }
</style>
